title: May 1, 2025
textContent:
---clair obscur---

Tenenenewnew

Na LSS talaga ako HAHAHAHAHA. Ababayu my bby! I'm playing what might be the best game I've ever experienced in my life right now, and I'm so so so lucky!

Because I have a GF that's very supportive of me! Pati yung mga tiktoks rugo abt the game, sinesend mo sakin! I really love how you also take a huge amount of interest sa hobbies ko! Yung ibang mga jowa ayaw nila naglalaro yung jowa nila, pero yung bby ko apaka supportive talaga! And you not only allow me to enjoy the game, you also try your best to involve yourself with how I enjoy the game HUHUHUHU LORD I'M SO LUCKY! ABABAYU MY BUNION BBYY!

I also try my best too to take interest in your hobbies (tho tbh, effortless naman yun kase halos pareho naman talaga hobbies naten HAHAHAHAHA) kase I also want to show you how much I support your hobbies!! I love you so much my bby! ABABAYU MWAAA!

P.S. Pangalawang letter na pala to this month about jow supportive you are HAHAHAHA yaan mo na ganyan talaga swerte ako sa jowa ko ano magagawa ko HAHAHA MWAA
